      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not like a heavy drinker or anything. i just meant like, if i have one glass of red wine with my pill at night, won't that just help me drift off faster? it feels like a tiny amount wouldn't really reach those 'dangerous' levels you're talking about, right?",
